: : Rodimus Prime : :
Rodimus took notice of Maxima comeing at him. He recognized the voice from the past.
Rodimus Prime: Can't say I'm happy to see you functioning. Now out of my way you Decepticon b*tch!
Maxima's attack had a very big flaw. Although she managed to slice a bit of Rodimus' hood, she failed to realize what a sports care going at speeds over 200mph would do. He simply plowed into her without careing in the least for the Decepticon femme. This would surely cause some heavy damage to Maxima.
 EmprzAnastazia@... wrote:arriving soon enough after Carnation....

She landed ready for combat. Another time she wished she had her old style form. But, her claws extended, her fang showed. The only other thing was her tail... it still attached to her, she would not use it... not yet. 

Her clear blue optics glared at Rodimus. "Well, well.. Rodimus Prime. I'm rather surprised to see you... functioning! But.. that can easily be REMEDIED!" 

She leapt at Rodimus, ready to attack him in a vicious primal rage, her claws slashing at him.
